        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This dust is created from the powdered bones of ensnared rabbits and other woodland creatures that died from fright. When inhaled, it pollutes the victim\u2019s mind with fear, awakening an unshakable prey response that sees danger lurking in every shadow.",
